				<td colspan="2"><span>Your wrists are your weakest point, they have good charisma yes but neither has any hp and hp will be more important later on.  You can compensate the loss of charisma by buying skyflow stones pretty cheap and having a friend cut them for you into + 12 cha.  By 62 you won't be able to solo for regular exp anymore and hp will be more important than charisma.  Don't know any names for exact pieces, just find a few wrists with moderate hp.
<br />

<br />
** also think you should update your geomancer's earring with earring of solcstice,  3-4k if you buy all the parts and turn it in, decent stats with ft 1 bonus.</span></td>
